name: clipper
description: I was working in a cafe as a dishwasher. it was the first time i figured out i can paint using my phone in my break time. it was chef Ehsan's lighter and he was so protective of that because lighters used to vanish in the cafe :))) i drew this on my sony Xperia LT26i scrached screen using andriod paintfree app. no layers, no photo transforms.because the app has a limited size i just took screenshot of my work.
